Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.52,0:01:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It was 2016 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.73,0:01:32.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The thing people lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:34.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,in other words, the complementation of the mind is unfolding.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,However, there's too little time to describe the entire process.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Therefore, we will discuss the complementation of the mind of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.36,0:01:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,one single boy named Ikari Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Case 3: In the case of Ikari Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:45.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That I disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:48.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, I can disappear because I feel that I am useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:49.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I am useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,After all, I am a useless child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody cares about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:02:00.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You run away considering nobody cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You fear to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:05.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You fear to be disliked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You fear to see the weakness within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right. We are the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Our mind lacks something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So we fear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So we worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.32,0:02:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So we are trying to be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.57,0:02:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We are trying to complement by the instrumentality of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the instrumentality project.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One cannot live without being surrounded by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:29.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One cannot live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One is always unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Causing hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Causing sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:38.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Causing the wish to feel anothers' mind and body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Causing the wish to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.09,0:02:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A human is made of weak and fragile materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.01,0:02:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The mind and body are also made of weak and fragile materials.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So it is necessary to complement by the instrumentality of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.94,0:02:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's no other way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.94,0:02:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I might live to know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,For whom do you live?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Obviously, for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Probably for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You enjoy your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You enjoy your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.46,0:03:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Of course yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You enjoy your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want to do anything not enjoyable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You dislike to be sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You dislike hardships?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. Do you blame for running away from something I hate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.36,0:03:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:40.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why won't you run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If I ran away, it would be more painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.07,0:03:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You ran away from something painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It was painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:49.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you know the pain, then everything's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You may run away if it's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can run away from something you truly hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, I don't. I don't want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.05,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No. I shall not run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's because you already know that running away will be more painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.51,0:04:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know how painful it is to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.81,0:04:11.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So you don't want to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I said, if I ran away, nobody would care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't desert me! Please! Don't desert me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.73,0:04:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Obeying the words of others, that's his way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right! Otherwise, I would be deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You fear to be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are trying to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not only you but also others are hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everybody feels hardships.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You think so, because it's easier for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shut up! That has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,People don't care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And you always desert your value.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And you try to think yourself valueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:59.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thinking that, doing nothing, one would not be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:02.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,People try to keep themselves by being praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody accepts me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are trying to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, I have to pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You've been trying to think yourself valueless since the very begining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, it's not so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are trying to think so, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am valueless. I have nothing to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So you pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:31.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Piloting Eva lets me be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Piloting Eva lets me be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:38.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Before piloting Eva, I had nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.69,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The fact that I pilot Eva lets me stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have nothing. NOTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The value to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I don't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,THUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate you! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Me hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry, but I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.05,0:06:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.14,0:06:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate you.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate everything you are.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, everybody hates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,People probably hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:26.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are trying to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NO. Because I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, you are trying to think that others hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.53,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate, I hate I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, I am praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am praised when I pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I was praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I was praised by people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Which is your true mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.80,0:06:55.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know, or, both of them are my true minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So you pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have nothing but Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Otherwise you cannot keep yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's true that Eva Unit One is part of your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you depend on Eva too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Eva itself will be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.03,0:07:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Eva will be all of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The true yourself will be nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's OK. I've had nothing from the begining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.54,0:07:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've been learning cello, but got no results.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You just didn't discipline yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, now that I can pilot Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:31.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, when you lose Eva, you can do nothing, like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why do you pilot Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because it's all of me.
