Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Rain, gloomy mood, just like my mood. I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The sinking sun, fading life, my hope. I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Morning, the beginning of today, the beginning of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,a bad day. I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Blue sky. Something warm, something unusual,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,something horrible. Something useless. I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:17.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you hope for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:19.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hate anxiety?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hate peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:24.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What I fear is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Rejection
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What I need is,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Contact and Approval
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,May I stay by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.78,0:08:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,May I stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you love me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.16,0:08:42.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want to go to your mom's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:43.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't you want to go to your dad's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I fear to be hated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I would disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.93,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,To erase anxiety.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,To erase sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're not happy are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.89,0:09:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,For that, I need.. I need my value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,In order to be appreciated, in order not to be deserted,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.53,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I need my VALUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That is what you must admit by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You must admit your own value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So you pilot Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't have any value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't have the value worth living.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then what am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:31.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.13,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What? it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:39.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The shape that I show to others...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The symbol representing Shinji
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:53.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, one needs the blockade of mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This, and this, and this, all these are the representation of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.98,0:09:49.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nothing but the things that make others recognize me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.19,0:09:57.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is me? The true me? The false me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are you. Yet, you have your own region and border.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:07.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's see. My clothes, my shoes, my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Those are part of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The things linked together by your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:16.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The thing that I think myself, that is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am nothing but myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.39,0:10:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, I don't understand. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What am I? What am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody understands me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You idiot! That's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody ever understands you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The one that takes care of you, and the one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that understands you is nobody but yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.91,0:10:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But still I don't have myself, so I don't understand myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.46,0:10:55.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's no way to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:56.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.51,0:10:58.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are still unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The present you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The people around the present you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The environment that surrounds the present you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,None of them last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your time is always flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are made of the changing world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:17.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are the thing that may change according to
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,your own mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What? The world with nothing. The world with nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The world of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.70,0:11:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The world of freedom that would never be restrained by anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.92,0:11:35.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is this Freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. The world of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,As a result, there's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:42.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Unless I think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.22,0:11:44.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, unless you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:48.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell! I don't know what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't have your own image.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Too vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everything is vague.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:11:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The world in which you can do anything you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, you are uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't you know what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I give you a restriction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now you have a top and bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now you have lost one degree of freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now you have to stand on the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But you obtain a comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You get slightly easier in your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.72,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And you walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That is your will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is this my will?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The world with the bottom is the world surrounding you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, you can move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you wish, you can change the position of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:41.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The world does not keep the same position.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That changes through the time flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can also change.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:51.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The things that form you are your own mind and
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the world surrounding yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:55.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Since this is your own world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The real figure that you conceive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That is the reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.38,0:13:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is the world with nothing, the space with nothing, the world with nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The world with nothing but me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:11.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am less understanding myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I feel as if I am going to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My existence is fading away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because there's nobody but you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody but me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.57,0:13:24.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because you have no existence but that of yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.74,0:13:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can't figure out your own shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My image?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. You are getting to know your own shape through seeing the shapes of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Seeing the walls of others, you imagine yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You cannot see yourself unless there are others.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because there are others, I can exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If I'm alone, then I will be the same as everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.55,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There will be no difference between myself and nothing..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,By understanding the difference between you and others,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.68,0:13:57.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you form the image of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The very first other person is your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.11,0:14:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your mother is a different person from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:11.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. I am I. Yet, it's true that others form the shape of my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.08,0:14:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's right, Ikari Shinji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Man, you took a long time to figure it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:16.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stupid Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You wake up now. Stupid Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, it's you, Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You say "It's you Asuka?."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:33.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Every morning, I come to wake you up so you won't be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:37.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that how you thank a childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:44.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ah... I mean thanks, so, let me sleep a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What a lazy guy! Wake up! Wake up imediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh! NO! You, mean stupid horny guy! Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's morning. It's natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shinji is a lazy kid. He should be more grateful
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that Asuka comes to wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dear, you have to get ready too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:18.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're just like Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.31,0:15:24.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. It's always me who is scolded by Professor Fuyutsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,when you are late for a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's true, he's your biggest fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop saying stupid things. Change clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,hmmm, I see, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.25,0:15:40.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,OK, I know, you're such a pain in the ass sometimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:45.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, I am off, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bye! Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, how long are you going to keep reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:16:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,hmmm, I see. Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hear that today we also have a newcomer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:12.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, yes. This city will be the new capital city
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,after the capital transfer next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The population is increasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.83,0:16:21.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right. What kinda girl? I hope it's a cute girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Phew.. Late for school! It's very bad to be late for
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,school from the very first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, sorry, I am truly in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Really! Then you saw it? I mean the girl's panty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:17:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I did not intend to see but, only a moment,..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,WOW, What a lucky boy you are this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ouch! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.79,0:17:12.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Suzuhara, don't talk about such stupid things!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, water the plants. You are on duty this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What a noisy girl..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He will be controlled after he gets married, Touji will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You will as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:27.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How come you say I will be controlled?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,YES. I told nothing but the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are what you appear to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Asuka, You are always talking ..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So peaceful..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Teacher Misato is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Teacher Misato is looking real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.63,0:17:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That trio of fools, They're real idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stand up. Bow. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Boys be glad! Today, I'm going to introduce you to the transferee
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,everybody is talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:16.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am Ayanami Rei. Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You! You are that stupid guy that peeped at my panty this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.12,0:18:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,NO, Stop! Don't say such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's you that showed it to Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.54,0:18:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You moron, why do you cover that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you guys dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No! We're just childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop! It's school time. Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, You seem to be enjoying yourselves. I am curious as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.84,0:18:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've got it. This is also a world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A possiblity within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The me at the moment is not always the me as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There are many selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. There must be the me who is not the Eva pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.58,0:19:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thinking like that, the real world itself is not always bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.29,0:19:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The real world might not always be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:13.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's your mind that conceives that the reality is bad and hateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The mind which confuses the reality with the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:24.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The view angle, the position. If these are slightly different,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the things inside the mind will change a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.14,0:19:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The truths are as many as people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But there's only one truth that you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,which is formed by a narrowed view of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Formed by revised information to protect yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the twisted truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, yes. the view of the world that one can
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,have is quite small.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.87,0:19:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, one measures things only by one's own small measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One sees things with the truth given by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:55.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Happy on a sunny day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Gloomy on a rainy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:20:00.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If that's what you're taught, that's what you'll always think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Even so, you may enjoy rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your truth can be changed simply by the way you accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's how fragile truth is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The truth within a human is so cheap that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.85,0:20:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,people wish to know a deeper truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's only that you are not used to be liked by people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, you don't have to look upon other's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:31.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yet, don't you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.08,0:20:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You idiot! It's you that is always trying to think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:39.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Still, I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.30,0:20:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Those who hate themselves cannot love or trust others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am wicked, a coward, weak and ..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you know yourself, you can be kind to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I hate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.73,0:21:02.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, I might be able to love myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Maybe my life could have a greater value.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes. I am nothing but I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am I. I wish to be I.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want to continue existing in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am worth living here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.06,0:21:34.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:41.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.49,0:21:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!\NCongratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:53.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.62,0:21:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you, my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good bye, my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And to the all the children,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:01.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations!
